산업제어시스템(ICS: Industrial Control System)의 정상 데이터만 학습한 모델로, 비정상/사이버 공격 상황을 탐지하는 AI 모델을 개발하고 성능을 평가하는 대회이다.

학습 데이터 (Train)¶

time : 관측 시각
C01 ~ C79 : 센서 및 제어 상태 관측값 (79개)
각 파일은 시간 연속성을 가짐
정상 운영 상황만 포함 → 라벨 없음 (모두 정상)

검증 데이터 (Validation)¶

time : 관측 시각
C01 ~ C79 : 상태 관측값
attack : 공격 여부 라벨 (0: 정상, 1: 공격)
정상 + 공격 상황 모두 포함. 공격 라벨이 제공됨.

테스트 데이터 (Test)¶

time : 관측 시각
C01 ~ C79 : 상태 관측값

STRIDE = 10

In [12]:
def make_tf_dataset(X, window_size, stride, batch_size, shuffle=False):
    ds = tf.data.Dataset.from_tensor_slices(X)

    ds = ds.window(window_size, shift=stride, drop_remainder=True)
    ds = ds.flat_map(lambda w: w.batch(window_size))

    if shuffle:
        ds = ds.shuffle(1024)

    ds = ds.batch(batch_size).prefetch(tf.data.AUTOTUNE)
    ds = ds.map(lambda x: (x, x))
    return ds
In [13]:
train_ds = make_tf_dataset( X_train, window_size=WINDOW_SIZE, stride=STRIDE, batch_size=BATCH, shuffle=True )
val_ds = make_tf_dataset(   X_val,   window_size=WINDOW_SIZE, stride=STRIDE, batch_size=BATCH )

모델: LSTM AutoEncoder

In [14]:
LR = 1e-3

def build_lstm_ae(window_size, n_features):
    inp = tf.keras.Input(shape=(window_size, n_features))

    x = tf.keras.layers.LSTM(128, return_sequences=True)(inp)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.2)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LSTM(64, return_sequences=False)(x)

    x = tf.keras.layers.RepeatVector(window_size)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LSTM(64, return_sequences=True)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.2)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LSTM(128, return_sequences=True)(x)

    out = tf.keras.layers.TimeDistributed(tf.keras.layers.Dense(n_features))(x)
    return tf.keras.Model(inp, out, name="LSTM_AE")

model = build_lstm_ae(WINDOW_SIZE, n_features)
opt = tf.keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=LR, clipnorm=1.0)
model.compile(optimizer=opt, loss="mse")
model.summary()

윈도우별 재구성오차(Reconstruction Error)

In [17]:
offsets = np.arange(WINDOW_SIZE, dtype=np.int32)

# train 윈도우별 재구성오차 ----
train_starts = np.arange(0, len(X_train) - WINDOW_SIZE + 1, STRIDE, dtype=np.int32)

train_err_list = []
for i in range(0, len(train_starts), BATCH):
    batch_starts = train_starts[i:i + BATCH]                   
    index_matrix = batch_starts[:, None] + offsets[None, :]        
    batch_x = X_train[index_matrix]                                

    pred = model.predict_on_batch(batch_x)                           
    mse  = np.mean((pred - batch_x) ** 2, axis=(1, 2))               
    train_err_list.append(mse)

train_win_err = np.concatenate(train_err_list, axis=0)
In [18]:
# validation 윈도우별 재구성오차 ----
val_starts = np.arange(0, len(X_val) - WINDOW_SIZE + 1, STRIDE, dtype=np.int32)

val_err_list = []
for i in range(0, len(val_starts), BATCH):
    batch_starts = val_starts[i:i + BATCH]
    index_matrix = batch_starts[:, None] + offsets[None, :]
    batch_x = X_val[index_matrix]

    pred = model.predict_on_batch(batch_x)
    mse  = np.mean((pred - batch_x) ** 2, axis=(1, 2))
    val_err_list.append(mse)

val_win_err = np.concatenate(val_err_list, axis=0)
In [19]:
print("train_win_err:", train_win_err.shape, "val_win_err:", val_win_err.shape)

train_win_err: (92155,) val_win_err: (4315,)

임계치(threshold) 설정

In [40]:
threshold = np.max(train_win_err)
print(f"Threshold", threshold)

Threshold 25.729311

윈도우 점수 → 시점(point) 점수로 매핑 (agg='max')

In [30]:
n_points = len(X_val)
val_point_score = np.full(n_points, -np.inf, dtype=np.float32)

for w_score, st in zip(val_win_err, val_starts):
    seg = val_point_score[st:st + WINDOW_SIZE]
    val_point_score[st:st + WINDOW_SIZE] = np.maximum(seg, w_score)

minv = float(np.min(val_win_err))
val_point_score[~np.isfinite(val_point_score)] = minv

y_pred = (val_point_score > threshold).astype(np.int32)

roc = roc_auc_score(y_val, val_point_score)
pr  = average_precision_score(y_val, val_point_score)
f1  = f1_score(y_val, y_pred)

print("\n[Point-level metrics]")
print("ROC-AUC:", roc)
print("PR-AUC :", pr)
print("F1     :", f1)

print("\nConfusion Matrix:\n", confusion_matrix(y_val, y_pred))
print("\nClassification Report:\n", classification_report(y_val, y_pred, digits=4))
